              "audioEnd": 36.763
            },
            {
              "text": "The note suggested that the key belonged to a place where time stood still.",
              "audioStart": 37.625,
              "audioEnd": 41.237
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "Leo moved quickly toward the old church at the center of the village.",
              "audioStart": 42.1,
              "audioEnd": 45.263
            },
            {
              "text": "The building was silent, but he noticed a small lock on a side door which matched his key perfectly.",
              "audioStart": 46.125,
              "audioEnd": 51.362
            },
            {
              "text": "He wondered if the key would turn, or if he should wait for another sign.",
              "audioStart": 52.225,
              "audioEnd": 55.737
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "He pushed the key into the lock and turned it carefully.",
              "audioStart": 56.6,
              "audioEnd": 59.25
            },
            {
              "text": "The door opened to reveal a small room full of old records and forgotten letters.",
              "audioStart": 60.112,
              "audioEnd": 64.188
            },
            {
              "text": "Leo realized that he had found the true history of his family within this secret place.",
              "audioStart": 65.05,
              "audioEnd": 69.5
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "sentences": [
            {
              "text": "The sun was beginning to fall behind the mountains as he finished his search.",
